videos.description: Donovan Mitchell weaves through every Clippers defender in his path to get to the basket and readjusts to make a tough and-1 layup to get the crowd going.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell takes on all the Clippers for a tough and-1 bucket) 2021/06/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell takes on all the Clippers for a tough and-1 bucket

videos.description: Dwyane Wade leaps out of his seat and dishes out high-fives to Jazz fans after Bojan Bogdanovic knocks down a deep 3-pointer from the top of the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (D-Wade ecstatic after big Jazz bucket) 2021/06/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: D-Wade ecstatic after big Jazz bucket

videos.description: Rajon Rondo throws a perfect inbound pass to Ivica Zubac who elevates to flush an easy two-handed slam for the Clippers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Rondo finds Zubac for inbound alley-oop) 2021/06/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rondo finds Zubac for inbound alley-oop

videos.description: Rudy Gobert shows up big as he rejects Marcus Morris' 3-point shot in the final moments of the game to seal a 112-109 Game 1 win for the Jazz.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert swats Morris at the buzzer to seal Game 1 win for Jazz) 2021/06/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert swats Morris at the buzzer to seal Game 1 win for Jazz
